			<p>
				Sign up here: <a href="https://forms.gle/qzS8KsikQvbccG119">https://forms.gle/qzS8KsikQvbccG119</a>
			<p>
			<h1 class="imageflexcontent">
				{SITE_TITLE}
			</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome to the Peddie Math Club Website! We are a group of students passionate about spreading the love of mathematics to the Peddie community. 
			</p>
