				<ul>
					<li><a href="/blog/contest-24"><b>Math contests and competitions</b></a>, including the AMC and COMC</li>
					<li><a href="/blog/casino-night-24"><b>Casino Night</b></a>, a yearly Math Club tradition, on TBD</li>
